    {
      "id": "1914750c-f3ba-8068-b639-c5fb58d6d552",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "There is a research stream focusing on extracting learning strategies from multiple sources and multiple learning settings and checking how these different learning strategies map into overall performance. However, tow gaps are apparent: doing this for MOOCs is still relatively under-explored AND connections between uncovered strategies and psychological constructs is usually not performed.",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "1914750c-f3ba-8068-b639-c5fb58d6d552",
        "parent": {
          "type": "page_id",
          "page_id": "18c4750c-f3ba-804a-946f-c635264dddb5"
        },
        "created_time": "2025-02-05T14:49:00.000Z",
        "last_edited_time": "2025-02-05T14:51:00.000Z",
