    {
      "id": "1914750c-f3ba-80d9-8f34-d4eba9cefdad",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The paper uses process and sequence-mining techniques to detect learning strategies from MOOC logs and tries to map them to the Big Five personality traits. Results show 4 distinct learning strategies that were predicted by conscientiousness, emotional instability and agreeableness.  ",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "1914750c-f3ba-80d9-8f34-d4eba9cefdad",
        "parent": {
          "type": "page_id",
